            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "The Renaissance cathedral's tympanum was adorned with a depiction of the Last Judgment, a dramatic and powerful statement of religious doctrine."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
              "x": "The Romanesque doorway was framed by a sculpted tympanum depicting Christ in Majesty, surrounded by angels and saints."
            },
            {
              "cf": "",
